{"tid":153821,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[電腦白痴]電腦過熱問題","createTime":"2017-03-12T21:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T05:06:44.000Z","uid":9098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75f68307b9ce32953cd747f9bc2f2443f0c3f8a8","tid":153821,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:39:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的，想請教一下各位巴打關於電腦過熱既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟對電腦認識極淺，<br />\n盡可能將遇到既問題狀況講出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說每次用電腦既時候，<br />\n用緊Firefox睇下動畫上下連登果時，<br />\n部電腦都會好快熱到仆街，<br />\n最近發現熱到連個外罩都變咗少少形(頂部膠製)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摸落去仲十分辣手，絕對足夠將雞蛋煮熟既果種熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我個風扇又Run到、無塵，<br />\n發熱位我估係Hardisk(?)附近(直頭喺開機制後面)；<br />\n請問關唔關Firefox事？<br />\n因為小弟發現Firefox一開，就會將電腦粒cpu用到80%以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家用返Chrome，寧願佢食Ram都唔想用爆粒cpu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n腸唔油，但會真心答謝各位幫手推POST/解答既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ce8d3f6a8c5b1108aabc877c73dda77bcb4d8d","tid":153821,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:47:00.000Z","msg":"notebook嚟？<br />\n<br />\n換散熱鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce900201f6bb5ecf982c379f5c16ea10a4688f1","tid":153821,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T23:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>notebook嚟？<br />\n<br />\n換散熱鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，Desktop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家用Chrome又無咩問題，<br />\nkeep住10-20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas